# рџ“ё FaceTrack вЂ” PHP Snapshot Manager & Attendance Backend

> **`attendance.php`** вЂ” A single-file PHP backend that adds camera snapshot capture, a searchable image gallery, attendance logging, and student management to the AI Smart Attendance System.

---

## вњЁ What this file does

| Feature | Details |
|---|---|
| рџ“· **Live camera capture** | Uses browser `getUserMedia` API to stream webcam, lets you take JPEG snapshots with one click |
| рџ–јпёЏ **Snapshot gallery** | Grid view of all stored images, with download, delete, and lightbox zoom |
| рџ“‹ **Attendance log** | Date-filtered table with confidence scores, status badges, and linked snapshot thumbnails |
| рџ‘Ґ **Student management** | Add/search students, view per-student attendance percentage |
| рџ“Љ **Dashboard stats** | Live counts вЂ” enrolled students, present today, late, total snapshots |
| рџ¤– **AI engine bridge** | cURL ping to your Python Flask engine at `http://127.0.0.1:5000` вЂ” shows online/offline status |
| рџ› пёЏ **DB auto-setup** | Built-in SQL installer tab вЂ” creates all tables with one click |
| рџ“¤ **CSV export** | Export any day's attendance as a downloadable `.csv` |

