## рџ—„пёЏ Database schema

```sql
students        вЂ” id, name, roll_number, class, email, enrolled_at
attendance      вЂ” id, student_id, name, class, date, time_in, confidence, status, snapshot_file
snapshots       вЂ” id, filename, label, taken_at
```

