## рџ”’ Security notes for production

- Add HTTP Basic Auth or a session login check at the top of `attendance.php`
- Set `open_basedir` to restrict PHP file access
- Move the `snapshots/` folder outside the web root and serve via a PHP proxy
- Use prepared statements (already used throughout) вЂ” never interpolate user input into SQL

---

## рџ¤ќ Works alongside

- **`attendance_dashboard.html`** вЂ” the humanized frontend dashboard (same repo)  
- **Python Flask AI engine** вЂ” face recognition backend using OpenCV + LBPH  
- **OpenCV** вЂ” `cv2.VideoCapture` feeds frames to the recogniser  

